Sheila, don't stray away from me!"},{"lineNumber":175633,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ぎゅっと抱きついてろ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hold on to me tight!"},{"lineNumber":175634,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ははは、はいー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Haha, okay!"},{"lineNumber":175635,"originalJapaneseLine":"『5、4、3……』","translatedEnglishLine":"'5, 4, 3...'"},{"lineNumber":175636,"originalJapaneseLine":"「来るぞ来るぞ来るぞ来るぞぉぉぉお！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Here it comes, here it comes, here it comes, heeere it comes!"},{"lineNumber":175637,"originalJapaneseLine":"『2、1――","translatedEnglishLine":"'2, 1—'"},{"lineNumber":175638,"originalJapaneseLine":"　……0でございます』","translatedEnglishLine":"'...0 now.'"},

{"lineNumber":175639,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ランス城あたたたたたーーーーーっく！！！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance Castle atttttttt-tack!!!!"},{"lineNumber":175640,"originalJapaneseLine":"そして――","translatedEnglishLine":"And then—"},{"lineNumber":175641,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランス城は爆音を轟かせて、","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance Castle roared with a booming sound,"},

{"lineNumber":175642,"originalJapaneseLine":"ベズドグ山に激突した。","translatedEnglishLine":"and crashed into Mount Bezdug."},

{"lineNumber":175643,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ugh..."},

{"lineNumber":175644,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う〜〜〜〜ん……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Uuuuuuunnnn..."},

{"lineNumber":175645,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はっ！　な、なんだここ！？","translatedEnglishLine":"Hah! W-Where is this!?"},

{"lineNumber":175646,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あれからどうなった！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"What happened after that!?"},

{"lineNumber":175647,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むぎゅう……ら、ランス様……","translatedEnglishLine":"Mugyuu... L-Lance-sama..."},

{"lineNumber":175648,"originalJapaneseLine":"　苦しいですぅ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"It hurts..."},

{"lineNumber":175649,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああ、倒れてきた壁の下敷きになってるようだな。","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah, it looks like we're trapped under a fallen wall."},

{"lineNumber":175650,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うむむむ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ummm..."},

{"lineNumber":175651,"originalJapaneseLine":"「とりゃーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Toryaaah!"},

{"lineNumber":175652,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お、おお、これはまた……」","translatedEnglishLine":"O-oh, this is quite something..."},

{"lineNumber":175653,"originalJapaneseLine":"「結構な大惨事」","translatedEnglishLine":"A rather big disaster."},

{"lineNumber":175654,"originalJapaneseLine":"「アホですか貴方はーーッ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Are you an idiot or what?!"},
 
{"lineNumber":175655,"originalJapaneseLine":"「けほっ、けほっ……","translatedEnglishLine":"Keh, keh... (cough, cough)..."},

{"lineNumber":175656,"originalJapaneseLine":"　頭打ってしまいました……」","translatedEnglishLine":"I hit my head..."},

{"lineNumber":175657,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお、良かった良かった。","translatedEnglishLine":"Oh, that's good, that's good."},

{"lineNumber":175658,"originalJapaneseLine":"　君達も生きてたか」","translatedEnglishLine":"You all survived too, huh?"},

{"lineNumber":175659,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うう……ランス様、無茶しすぎです……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ugh... Lance-sama, you overdid it..."},

{"lineNumber":175660,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はあ……","translatedEnglishLine":"Hah..."},

{"lineNumber":175661,"originalJapaneseLine":"　怪我人と敵側の様子の調査を行います……」","translatedEnglishLine":"We need to check on the injured and investigate the enemy's status..."},

{"lineNumber":175662,"originalJapaneseLine":"軍師達が率先して、","translatedEnglishLine":"The strategists took the lead,"},

{"lineNumber":175663,"originalJapaneseLine":"城内で無事な人間の点呼がすぐさま行われた。","translatedEnglishLine":"and quickly took roll call of the unharmed inside the castle."},

{"lineNumber":175664,"originalJapaneseLine":"玉座の間に、無事だった人間と、","translatedEnglishLine":"In the throne room, those who were safe,"},

{"lineNumber":175665,"originalJapaneseLine":"各国の主要人物達が集められる。","translatedEnglishLine":"and the main figures from each country were gathered."},

{"lineNumber":175666,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やれやれ、まさか城ごと突撃するとは……","translatedEnglishLine":"Good grief, to think we charged with the whole castle..."},

{"lineNumber":175667,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いや、こうなってもおかしくなかった、か」","translatedEnglishLine":"No, maybe it wasn't so strange it ended like this."},

{"lineNumber":175668,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あいてて……","translatedEnglishLine":"Ouch ouch..."},

{"lineNumber":175669,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こりゃ、戦闘はちょいと無理そうだ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Looks like fighting's a bit impossible right now..."},

{"lineNumber":175670,"originalJapaneseLine":"「馬鹿体力の癖に怪我して身動き出来んとは、","translatedEnglishLine":"Despite your stupid stamina, you got injured and can't move,"},

{"lineNumber":175671,"originalJapaneseLine":"　本当にいいとこ一つも残ってないな」","translatedEnglishLine":"Not a single good point left in you."},

{"lineNumber":175672,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、面目ねえ……","translatedEnglishLine":"No, I'm ashamed..."},

{"lineNumber":175673,"originalJapaneseLine":"　言い訳はしねぇよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I won't make excuses."},

{"lineNumber":175674,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あんたが無茶するからでしょうが！」","translatedEnglishLine":"It's because you pushed yourself too hard!"},

{"lineNumber":175675,"originalJapaneseLine":"「パットンはみんなを守って怪我したのー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Patton got hurt trying to protect everyone—"},

{"lineNumber":175676,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それでも二人にも怪我させちまったからな……","translatedEnglishLine":"Still, I ended up hurting two others too..."},

{"lineNumber":175677,"originalJapaneseLine":"　面目ねぇってのはそういうことさ」","translatedEnglishLine":"That's what I mean by being ashamed."},

{"lineNumber":175678,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし、実際これからどうする？","translatedEnglishLine":"But seriously, what do we do now?"},

{"lineNumber":175679,"originalJapaneseLine":"　動けない奴は俺以外にも結構いるぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"There are quite a few besides me who can't move."},

{"lineNumber":175680,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そうですね……","translatedEnglishLine":"That's right..."},

{"lineNumber":175681,"originalJapaneseLine":"　残念ながら魔人討伐隊の半分ほどが……","translatedEnglishLine":"Unfortunately, about half of the demon extermination team..."},

{"lineNumber":175682,"originalJapaneseLine":"「敵の様子はどうなってる？」","translatedEnglishLine":"What's the status of the enemy?"},

{"lineNumber":175683,"originalJapaneseLine":"「動きが一切ありません。","translatedEnglishLine":"They aren't moving at all."},

{"lineNumber":175684,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おそらくかなり混乱してるようです」","translatedEnglishLine":"They must be quite confused."},

{"lineNumber":175685,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はははは！","translatedEnglishLine":"Hahaha!"},

{"lineNumber":175686,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんせ、味方すら混乱してるんだ、","translatedEnglishLine":"After all, even our allies are confused,"},

{"lineNumber":175687,"originalJapaneseLine":"　敵にはもっと混乱してもらわなくっちゃな」","translatedEnglishLine":"so the enemy should be confused even more."},

{"lineNumber":175688,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やかましい」","translatedEnglishLine":"Shut up."},

{"lineNumber":175689,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やっぱりここは皆さんの回復を待ってから、","translatedEnglishLine":"As expected, we should wait for everyone to recover,"},

{"lineNumber":175690,"originalJapaneseLine":"　改めて出撃を……」","translatedEnglishLine":"and then set out again..."}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ら、ランス様ぁ！？
「がははは！　シィル、俺から離れるなよぉ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahaha! Sheila, don't stray away from me!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぎゅっと抱きついてろ！」
「ははは、はいー！」
「来るぞ来るぞ来るぞ来るぞぉぉぉお！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Here it comes, here it comes, here it comes, heeere it comes!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……0でございます』
「ランス城あたたたたたーーーーーっく！！！！」
そして――
ランス城は爆音を轟かせて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle roared with a booming sound,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ベズドグ山に激突した。
「はっ！　な、なんだここ！？
あれからどうなった！？」
「むぎゅう……ら、ランス様……
苦しいですぅ……」
「ああ、倒れてきた壁の下敷きになってるようだな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, it looks like we're trapped under a fallen wall.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うむむむ……」
「とりゃーーー！」
「お、おお、これはまた……」
「結構な大惨事」
「アホですか貴方はーーッ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Are you an idiot or what?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「けほっ、けほっ……
頭打ってしまいました……」
「おお、良かった良かった。
君達も生きてたか」
「うう……ランス様、無茶しすぎです……」
「はあ……
怪我人と敵側の様子の調査を行います……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We need to check on the injured and investigate the enemy's status...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 軍師達が率先して、
城内で無事な人間の点呼がすぐさま行われた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and quickly took roll call of the unharmed inside the castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 玉座の間に、無事だった人間と、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the throne room, those who were safe,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各国の主要人物達が集められる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the main figures from each country were gathered.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やれやれ、まさか城ごと突撃するとは……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Good grief, to think we charged with the whole castle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、こうなってもおかしくなかった、か」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, maybe it wasn't so strange it ended like this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいてて……
こりゃ、戦闘はちょいと無理そうだ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Looks like fighting's a bit impossible right now...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「馬鹿体力の癖に怪我して身動き出来んとは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Despite your stupid stamina, you got injured and can't move,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本当にいいとこ一つも残ってないな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Not a single good point left in you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、面目ねえ……
言い訳はしねぇよ」
「あんたが無茶するからでしょうが！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's because you pushed yourself too hard!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「パットンはみんなを守って怪我したのー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Patton got hurt trying to protect everyone—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでも二人にも怪我させちまったからな……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Still, I ended up hurting two others too...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 面目ねぇってのはそういうことさ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what I mean by being ashamed.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし、実際これからどうする？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But seriously, what do we do now?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 動けない奴は俺以外にも結構いるぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are quite a few besides me who can't move.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうですね……
残念ながら魔人討伐隊の半分ほどが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Unfortunately, about half of the demon extermination team...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「敵の様子はどうなってる？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What's the status of the enemy?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「動きが一切ありません。
おそらくかなり混乱してるようです」
「はははは！
なんせ、味方すら混乱してるんだ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After all, even our allies are confused,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敵にはもっと混乱してもらわなくっちゃな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so the enemy should be confused even more.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やかましい」
「やっぱりここは皆さんの回復を待ってから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As expected, we should wait for everyone to recover,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 改めて出撃を……」

translationLines.description: Array of objects, each representing a line from the input

originalJapaneseLine.description: The original line in Japanese exactly as it was in the input

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English
